title: Maddie - the truth of the lie (Goncalo Amaral) (english version)
description:
Maddie - the truth of the lie

this book is banned in England (along with any other criticism of the McCanns, or questioning of their story concerning the disappearance of madeleine, their 3 yr old daughter from a portugese apartment in may 2007

a paper.hardbacked version in the english language has never been produced - i found a translation online, and have "fashioned" a cover for it-

MADDIE-THE TRUTH OF THE LIE...by GONCALO AMARAL (ENGLISH LANGUAGE VERSION)

in .MOBI, .EPUB & .PDF
